  <travelInformation><![CDATA[<p>All our holidays include return travel to resort either by flight or train and then the transfer to your accommodation.</p>
<p>Departures are on Saturdays with stays for 7 or 14 nights and flexible duration on any day departures are available with certain hotels</p>
<p>Private transfers and self drive options are available, call to book these. Parking (payable locally) for all cars is in Täsch.</p>
<p>If you have a valid lift pass you can get on the free bus which runs between the three base stations in Zermatt (Sunegga, Gornergrat or the Matterhorn Glacier Express)</p>]]></travelInformation>
